yoff", "username": "LayoffAI"}, "content": "Amazon: 30,000 Americans laid off. 12,000 H-1B visas approved. Same window.\n\nMeta: 16,000 out. 5,000 visas in.\n\nMicrosoft: 3,426 out. 5,000 visas in.\n\nAI is taking the jobs. And the ones AI doesn\u2019t take, they\u2019re offshoring.\n\nThis is accelerating rapidly before our eyes.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 4867}, "images": [{"width": 2160, "heightRatio": 105, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HEY12tGa8AAf11U.png", "height": 2283}], "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 249, "created": 1774638000000, "id": "2037605574678806787", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2027441478897963009/s35ppvFs_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Official Layoff", "username": "LayoffAI"}, "content": "To hire an H-1B worker, companies must sign a federal form saying they can't find qualified Americans.\n\nWe pulled 15 years of filings. Analyzed the top 5.\n\n314,100 times they said no Americans available.\n\n99,000 times they fired Americans.\n\nSigned under oath. Exposed by data.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 13805}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZ3hLxn6", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 79, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8518398, "raw_content": "", "author": "TateDemarcus", "created": 1774663835912, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "MinneMAGA", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "cdn.5mind.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZ3hLxn6.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://cdn.5mind.com/uploads/production/Xp9Mac5LPGEVHPRCUM0m0/image/8ek5wmGZJLNzdwy_Uq8_-.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/0oMyPkLlKSNkE01W.jpeg", "width"